<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gas Leak Detection System</title>

    <style>
        *{
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
            box-sizing:border-box;
            font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        body{
            background:#f4f6f9;
            color:#333;
        }

        header{
            background:#0d6efd;
            color:white;
            text-align:center;
            padding:40px 20px;
        }

        section{
            max-width:1000px;
            margin:auto;
            padding:30px;
        }

        .card{
            background:white;
            padding:20px;
            margin:20px 0;
            border-radius:10px;
            box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
        }

        h2{
            color:#0d6efd;
            margin-bottom:15px;
        }

        ul{
            margin-left:20px;
        }

        footer{
            text-align:center;
            padding:20px;
            background:#222;
            color:white;
        }

        .btn{
            display:inline-block;
            margin-top:15px;
            padding:10px 20px;
            background:#0d6efd;
            color:white;
            text-decoration:none;
            border-radius:5px;
        }

        .btn:hover{
            background:#084298;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>🔥 Gas Leak Detection System</h1>
    <p>Arduino Uno + MQ-4 Gas Sensor + Python Dashboard</p>
</header>

<section>

<div class="card">
<h2>About Project</h2>
<p>
This project detects methane gas using an MQ-4 sensor connected to an Arduino Uno.
Sensor readings are sent to a Python dashboard through serial communication for
real-time monitoring and gas leak alerts.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Features</h2>

<ul>
<li>Real-Time Gas Monitoring</li>
<li>Python Live Dashboard</li>
<li>Gas Leak Alerts</li>
<li>CSV Data Logging</li>
<li>Arduino-Python Serial Communication</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Hardware Used</h2>

<ul>
<li>Arduino Uno</li>
<li>MQ-4 Gas Sensor</li>
<li>USB Cable</li>
<li>Breadboard</li>
<li>Jumper Wires</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Software Used</h2>

<ul>
<li>Arduino IDE</li>
<li>Python 3</li>
<li>VS Code</li>
<li>Matplotlib</li>
<li>PySerial</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Project Repository</h2>

<p>
Upload your Arduino code, Python dashboard, images, and README to this repository.
</p>

<a class="btn" href="https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/Gas-Leak-Detection-System">
View GitHub Repository
</a>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

Developed by <b>Mayank Nanaware</b><br>
MIT Vishwaprayag University, Solapur

</footer>

</body>
</html>
